item.title: CVE-2022-41275|2024-08-03T12:42:45.882Z -- sap -- solution%20manager%20%28enterprise%20search%29
item.description: In SAP Solution Manager (Enterprise Search) - versions 740, and 750, an unauthenticated attacker can generate a link that, if clicked by a logged-in user, can be redirected to a malicious page that could read or modify sensitive information, or expose the user to a phishing attack, with little impact on confidentiality and integrity.
